      "content": "hey so im 20 weeks pregnant and i have this really bad sinus infection that just wont go away. my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i was thinking about taking some sudafed to help with the congestion but i wasnt sure if that's okay to do right now? or is there something else i should take instead?",
